Description: Migrate From StealthAUDIT to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor

Hello Team,

We currently have Netwrix Auditor and would like to stand up a new Server with the current Netwrix Auditor we have plus Sharepoint auditing.

Is there any chance someone can arrange a meeting with me and I can show you what we have on our current Netwrix environment and I can go ahead and stand up new servers and so forth.

Thank you
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Saqib Sharif, Daniel West

What We've Learned Updated: The customer wants to migrate from Netwrix Auditor to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor. They want to do the configurations themselves but they dont want to engage Professional Support team.

Next Steps Updated: Documentation link has been shared. They will setup the server and let us know if they require any help. If the customer doesn't get back to us, I will follow up with them by Friday 21st Feb, 2025
